rating_comment: Maria's Homestay is the perfect choice for travellers looking to find a resting place in Siliguri before going further up North all while experiencing genuine hospitality. Highly recommended for a memorable & relaxing stay!
This was my second stay and next time im in West Bengal, this will be my place of choice. Great food, great company and a great stopping point on the way to or back from the Himalayas.
My favorite part was having breakfast with them in the morning, we talked about the area, swapped stories, and overall had great conversations over the delicious homemade food.

It's not often that you meet such hospitable and warm hosts. I received more than I'd asked, genuine love.
Thank you so much Maria! My stay has been pleasant because of you
Maria is a great host. She prepared some tasty home cooked meals. I highly recommend the homestay.
